{"tid":18022,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【我覺得我冇錯】蘇永康勸梁游快啲醒覺：背祖忘宗分裂國家唔做得㗎","createTime":"2016-12-02T05:19:49.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-02T06:31:05.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a6c58f606d81530e4c46d237ac58d4abe7dc4394","tid":18022,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T05:19:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161201/large/1480606264_6fee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161201%2Flarge%2F1480606264_6fee.jpg&h=f4d52069&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就前日發表之「我唔想生個梁天恆(梁頌恆)，我唔想生個游蕙禎，我要佢識分莊閒」，面對網民強烈反彈，問他是否堅持言論冇錯？阿公話：「冇錯，我覺得我冇錯。當然社會嘅事一定有正反面，大部份人支持話我係啱。」<br />\n<br />\n「今朝(即昨晨)我去入油，個阿嫂都話：『阿公，你真係講得啱，嗰兩個0靚仔真係乜乜物物。』我話唔緊要，人哋後生仔，畀啲時間佢哋，或者佢哋未識呢，年輕人應該畀機會，希望佢哋快啲醒覺，我始終維持嗰句，背祖忘宗分裂國家係唔做得㗎。」<br />\n<br />\n問到阿公係咪選民，今年有冇投票？佢話：「有，我話埋你知我投畀邊個都得，我投畀王維基，因為我同佢做過事，雖然好多人話唔喜歡佢政綱袋住先，但我同佢做過嘢，知道佢係實幹人，袋住先慢慢同政府傾，都仲有得傾呀，依家係傾都冇得傾，大佬，立法會流會流咗幾多次呀，我哋有份納稅㗎。」"},{"pid":"d687b12291ece2c999621e6f96a8b852297d49be","tid":18022,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T05:21:53.000Z","msg":"點解佢要縮起個膊?"},{"pid":"b245471a8a112a9a613f22720461c97fba38a6ff","tid":18022,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T05:22:29.000Z","msg":"祖宗？宗你老母"},{"pid":"98c8bbe62ce141f841629889b1d851897424876c","tid":18022,"uid":22680,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T05:23:10.000Z","msg":"吸毒得唔得"},{"pid":"560f2c14a34f7d415446cc466100f9a680846175","tid":18022,"uid":6864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T05:26:11.000Z","msg":"按佢邏輯 美加澳 三個人全部要冚國鏟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f07f3c721fbc37daa15afd91d60b7db9fd4b4898","tid":18022,"uid":6864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T05:27:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>按佢邏輯 美加澳 三<span style=\"color: red;\">國</span>人全部要冚國鏟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"7f5d404799258ae4e697bc54f3404c2cfb0b93b4","tid":18022,"uid":88,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T05:27:59.000Z","msg":"道友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67fef33cdb4e99425715ee8f525232583db76d44","tid":18022,"uid":45650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T05:29:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>按佢邏輯 美加澳 三<span style=\"color: red;\">國</span>人全部要冚國鏟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n按佢邏輯, 孫中山都係一個大仆街"},{"pid":"faa9e123fecbfdcfb61c3f78190ab3da0cda971a","tid":18022,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T05:29:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>按佢邏輯 美加澳 三<span style=\"color: red;\">國</span>人全部要冚國鏟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n全國華人強制返回大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n否則誅九族<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5550e556de86eba63922d92ecf7a25c5361f77f1","tid":18022,"uid":37951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T05:30:26.000Z","msg":"祖宗?應該係中華民國 <br />\n唔會係共匪國"},{"pid":"93cd18b990d2443270d406d317452b63f330dc10","tid":18022,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T05:31:39.000Z","msg":"弱智就出少句聲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aac42eae5b566f4a5293ffce3264c1beb620cc0c","tid":18022,"uid":41152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T05:31:45.000Z","msg":"唔知今屆第一次流會係咩人搞出黎既呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"